{"tid":2049086,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"彭博社：澳洲投行麥格理提早退租中環國金部份樓面 據稱是配合在家辦公政策","createTime":"2020-06-03T08:20:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-03T10:06:24.000Z","uid":21470,"like":21,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"38b6facd8085fcb120b3cb5b288003516acf18ff","tid":2049086,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T08:20:26.000Z","msg":"彭博社指麥格理提早退租國金部份樓面<br />\n03.06.2020 15:50<br />\n<br />\n彭博通訊社報道，澳洲投資銀行麥格理集團提早退租中環國金一期的部份樓面，麥格理發言人拒絕置評。報道引述土地註冊處資料，麥格理將會在9月底前，提早退租20樓13個室，但仍然會繼續租用20樓其餘地方，以及另外三層樓面。<br />\n<br />\n報道指，不少金融機構檢討全球各地租用辦公室的情況，以配合疫情下員工在家中工作的新常態，希望減省成本。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1298430&amp;csid=261_368\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1298430%26csid%3D261_368&d=ZttPR3oQiG8LQafLEcup%2BClZyh30VB0jKt3ffwT98zY%3D&h=0bfaa366\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1298430&amp;csid=261_368</a>"},{"pid":"04fcb771211270feb3b3d8102c6e6ab12073ab6a","tid":2049086,"uid":262389,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T08:23:10.000Z","msg":"[行動POST]615全民放假悼念日<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2046213\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2046213</a>"},{"pid":"7076e7cdf82a17eb29d58cfd47a1f60e84968ca5","tid":2049086,"uid":90601,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T08:23:18.000Z","msg":"不要說：撤僑 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n試著說：wfh  <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8df5b30a3832e4bb2c724ef2109c0f04ccc0b881","tid":2049086,"uid":254383,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T08:25:37.000Z","msg":"Cut cost 多啲"},{"pid":"5cbb899a0bcb82923d956437ae308a7551608c1b","tid":2049086,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03